{"tid":1499152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月30日 重光74周年默站 自己香港自己救","createTime":"2019-08-23T15:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T10:48:57.000Z","uid":232306,"like":95,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"efbaee6d996598860208200ca142e03877b7b342","tid":1499152,"uid":232306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"香港之路證明了行禮如儀式活動，門檻低而具團結感召效用。我地需要繼續喚醒記憶，塑造經歷，充分運用本港歷史資產，鞏固香港人身份認同，並向國際展示。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>8月30日（五）晚上8時<br />\n中環和平紀念碑<br />\n默站，掩右眼/MockingJay手勢。</strong><br />\n<br />\n歷史背景：1945年8月30日，皇家海軍上將夏慤率領特遣艦隊扺港，結束3年零8個月日據時代，香港重光，浴火重生，下周五係74周年。<br />\n<br />\n過往中共多次詆毁1941年香港保衛戰駐港英軍及本地軍民的貢獻，更轉為褒獎東江縱隊，偷換正朔，竊據二戰勝利者一席。<br />\n<br />\n如今義民負傷被捕者眾，更有死傷，堪稱當世的香港保衛戰。默站係我地上承烈士遺志，抱持義憤，繼續奮鬥的儀式。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n小小建議，望大家斧正。如果文宣組覺得合適，望能加入香港人日程表。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CwbYGEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwbYGEm.jpg&h=cbf6e2e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4RvbhcH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4RvbhcH.jpg&h=107bd61d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pn71Eq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPn71Eq4.jpg&h=9139a409&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbb796331e251e4cbfd7af4eeb0e232c02eab46d","tid":1499152,"uid":103239,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"而家就係我地既香港保衛戰！ Support!"},{"pid":"f588a3913ab1b45c7546d8b5ac2e46c823bbc605","tid":1499152,"uid":275502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"60e8d16db716a140e75d01d5adc3e7b1e72e9a93","tid":1499152,"uid":22099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904b1eec6ae5c2e85cf19a60bf622c50c1f281a3","tid":1499152